Access Indicators:
    🔒 - Admin Only 
    🔑 - Authorization Required 
    🌐 - Open 

/api/v1
├──/keys
│  ├──🔒 GET: Read all api keys 
│  ├──🔑 POST: Create new api key
│  └──/{keyId}
│     ├──🔒 PUT: Update api key by id 
│     └──🔒 DELETE: Delete api key by id 
├──/users
│  ├──🔒 GET: Read all users 
│  ├──🌐 POST: Create new user AND Profile
│  └──/{userId}
│     ├──🔑 GET: Read user by id
│     ├──🔑 PUT: Update user by id
│     ├──🔑 DELETE: Delete user by id
│     ├──/keys
|     │  └──🔑 GET: Read a user's full API key history 
│     ├──/posts
│     │  └──🔑 GET: Read all of a user's posts
│     └──/comments
│        └──🔑 GET: Read all of a user's comments
├──/profiles
│  ├──🔑 GET: Read all profiles
│  └──/{username}
│     ├──🔑 GET: Read profile by username
│     ├──🔑 PUT: Update profile by username
│     ├──🔑 DELETE: Delete profile by username
│     └──/public
│        └──🌐|🔑 GET: Read public profile by username
├──/blogs
│  ├──🌐 GET: Read all blogs
│  ├──🔑 POST: Create new blog
│  └──/{blogCategory}
│     ├──🌐 GET: Read blog by category
│     ├──🔑 PUT: Update blog by category
│     ├──🔑 DELETE: Delete blog by category
│     └──/posts
│        └──🌐 GET: Read all of a blog's posts
├──/posts
│  ├──🌐 GET: Read all posts
│  ├──🔑 POST: Create new post
│  └──/{postId}
│     ├──🌐 GET: Read post by id
│     ├──🔑 PUT: Update post by id
│     ├──🔑 DELETE: Delete post by id
│     ├──/comments
│     │  └──🌐 GET: Read all of a post's comments
│     └──/reactions
│        └──🌐 GET: Read all of a post's reactions
├──/comments
│  ├──🔒 GET: Read all comments
│  ├──🔑 POST: Create new comment
│  └──/{commentId}
│     ├──🔑 PUT: Update comment by id
│     ├──🔑 DELETE: Delete comment by id
│     ├──/replies
│     │  └──🌐 GET: Read all of a comment's replies
│     └──/reactions
│        └──🌐 GET: Read all of a comment's reactions
└──/reactions
   ├──🔒 GET: Read all reactions
   ├──🔑 POST: Create new reaction
   └──/{reactionId}
      ├──🔑 PUT: Update reaction by id
      └──🔑 DELETE: Delete reaction by id
